JJ the Boonirat,<br><br>
Your story of the bumper sticker is about the most wonderful thing I have heard in a long time. I am beginning to realize that there are people out there who care. I had a similar experience when I hung my decorations in my office four months ago. It was real tough to do that, and for a while people did not know what to say, but little by little the reactions were very much the opposite of my worst fears. Being in &quot;exile&quot; for so long really takes its toll.<br><br>
Doc Del,<br><br>
